                <mxCell id="118" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; line-height: 90%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Why Vheexa?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 90%;&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 18px; line-height: 90%;&quot;&gt;To Enhance My Developement Skills.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 24px; line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;Who Want to Use Vheexa?&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;Clients: Who Want to Rent Vehicles.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Individuals and Companies: Who Want to Rent Their Vehicles.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 24px; line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;What Does Vheexa Do?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;Making Renting Process Easier for Both Clients, Individual and Companies&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 24px; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 24px; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;User&#39;s story line!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;# As a Partner&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;I want to sign up when I sign up I wait the platform&lt;br&gt;to send me a payament gate so I can pay the fee&lt;br&gt;but if the info i provide were wrong&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;i want them to send me an email contians 2 componenets and what is wrong&lt;br&gt;1st what is wrong and why&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;2nd the OTP code for security&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;3rd a url lead to the edit page where i edit the mess info and correct them&lt;br&gt;if somehow i entered that url and miss out the OTP code&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;and i only have 3 chances if i missed them all&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;a new OTP code generate&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;and resend to me and so on for 3 times then the the device is requesting&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;is blocked unless the i chat with cutomer support and gave them reasons why&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;i missed all that times.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 18px; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;after i finish everything&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;i want to log in, when i try to log in for i recive a OTP code and if&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;i missed 3 time a new one generated and if i missed it all again for 3 times&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;the device trying to log in is blocked unless&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 18px; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;chat with cutomer support&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 18px; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;and give them reasons why&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;i missed all that times.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;so after i&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;am logged in i&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;can updated some info,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 18px; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;but some infos required me to wait till&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 18px; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;the customer support check every updates and accept them&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 18px; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;and whether i update a sensitive data or not i get a notification with&lt;br&gt;OTP code if i got it wrong for 3 time i recive a new OTP code for also&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 18px; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;3 times and if all wrong device requesting is blocked like when i sign up&lt;br&gt;after i set it right it takes my request to waiting board if sensitive&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 18px; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;or just update if nomral data&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;i can also create, read, update, delete and search my own&amp;nbsp;vehicles&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;when i delete i get are you sure popup&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;i can report clients and rate them as well or even block them from seeing my&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;vehicles again and when i rate them other partners can see the rating of that&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;clients and only partners not clients cuz clients would get nothing if they&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;know that this one is good or not, not like partners where they should know&lt;br&gt;so they can cancle the clients booking or even block the clients who are&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;less than 3 stars which each client is 5 stars max and 0 min&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; background-color: transparent; line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;Clients Can:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; background-color: transparent; line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;- Manange and Edit Personal Data&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;- Search&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;and&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;Filter for Vehicles&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;- Rent Vehicles&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;- R&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;ate&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;and&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Comment Vehicles&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;- See&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Vehicles Owners Data&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;- R&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;ate&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;and&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Comment Owners&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;- Report Vehicles Owners&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;Partners Can:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;- CRUDS Vheicles&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;- Block and Report Clients&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: wrap; line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;What Can be Enhanced in The Next 5 Years?&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;fontFamily=Comic Sans MS;fontStyle=0;fontColor=default;fillColor=none;sketch=1;curveFitting=1;jiggle=2;" parent="1" vertex="1">
